  "title": "Marketing Executive (Health and Wellness) - 0220",
  "description": "<p><strong>Marketing Executive</strong></p><p>Working hour: Mon - Fri 9.00 am to 06.00 pm.<br />Salary: $2,600 - $3,200<br />Location: Bugis (2 mins walk from Bugis MRT)</p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Manage and create content, visuals, and collateral for marketing campaigns.</p></li><li><p>Create prospect database from multiple sources for demand generation.</p></li><li><p>Online research and B2B prospecting.</p></li><li><p>Create content for social media (digital marketing – YouTube, Facebook, WhatsApp, Instagram) image and video editing.</p></li><li><p>Respond to customer enquiries and market company products.</p></li><li><p>Update databases and share testimonials/reports with clients.</p></li><li><p>Enhance and update company websites.</p></li><li><p>Monitor enquiries and respond appropriately.</p></li><li><p>Actively market and participate in company and third-party seminars and conferences.</p></li><li><p>Formulate and run marketing campaigns.</p></li><li><p>Prompt and effective handling of client queries.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum of 3 years of marketing experience.</p></li><li><p>Experience in digital marketing/online platform content creation</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office, Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, Canva, Adobe and other relevant visual creation software is mandatory.</p></li></ul><p>Chan Kai Wen Reg R23114137<br />THE SUPREME HR ADVISORY PTE LTD<br />EA No: 14C7279</p>",
